Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.33,sign_25783_365_Homosapiens,SIGN CENTER,0000,0000,0000,,Homosapiens
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.15,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We made it to the semifinals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.30,Default,SHIBAGAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:07.09,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,So, Yamamoto the manager seemed flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:12.33,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He wanted to know who \Nwas trying to buy it for 900 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:14.69,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,He was heading to a warehouse \Nat the harbor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.65,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely connected to Yano, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:22.39,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Was the boss's classmate's \Ndaughter in the dash cam data?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:26.17,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I checked, but I don't know \Nwhich passenger she would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.65,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not like I can show the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:31.21,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.67,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna rob a bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.19,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Sorry, I wasn't listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.10,sign_26834_378_Recording_1_wav,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304,164)}Recording 1.wav
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.10,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently my friend is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.85,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rob a bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.42,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid? How, in this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:52.26,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, I'm going to rob someone \Nwho's at the bank to make a withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.71,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:56.07,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Is the risk-return worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.69,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody walks around with that much cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:19:02.29,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,It's worth the risk. After all, \Nhe'll have one billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:05.08,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:10.37,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a week or two to get \Nenough cash for a large withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.54,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,They're supposed to contact me \Nwhen that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:18.52,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,They'll let me know who's receiving \Nhow much cash on what day at what time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.45,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,because I've bribed a bank employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:23.35,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,And then you're free to do \Nwhat you want with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.34,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's when \Nthe real crime begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.99,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the number one \Nbillion yen come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:33.24,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,The bank in question exchanges \Nlottery tickets for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:36.54,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who wins a large \Namount has to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.38,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, nobody would withdraw \Nthat much money in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:42.48,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,But recently, someone has \Nappeared on the internet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.58,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,claiming to have won one billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.36,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's probably aware of him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:51.00,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Because I demanded one \Nbillion from Yamamoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.32,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Yano will go after that guy \Nfor his one billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:56.94,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if they'll threaten him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.77,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,but they'll force him to withdraw the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.89,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for that opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.71,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you call fishing \Nin troubled waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:08.93,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Can you trust someone \Nwho makes that claim online?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.14,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,If it's fake, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:13.42,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somebody{\i0} won one billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.61,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Yano and his crew will find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.68,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,How much is one billion yen in cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.65,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be easily stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:23.96,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,It weighs about 100 kilos. \NNot impossible to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.24,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt the bank employees will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.77,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have other allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.49,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Among the police, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.20,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:35.06,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,You've been asking some very thoughtful \Nand expository questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.46,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Like you're trying to get me to commit \Nto answers for a third party to listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.11,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting involved in a major crime here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.68,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I want to know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:48.07,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Who, huh? I'm sure you have some idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:50.33,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't. Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.73,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Daimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.36,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:56.34,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,The older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.40,sign_30130_427_Recording_1_wav,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Recording 1.wav
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.40,sign_30167_428_End_Recording,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,End Recording
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:03.01,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kakihana your missing friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.91,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.26,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for him \Nwhere I think I might find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.41,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready to go anytime. \NStay nimble and alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:13.34,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't found skull mask \Nor Kabasawa yet, either—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:16.84,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like your henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.05,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.75,Default,SALARYMAN,0000,0000,0000,,You could definitely see half her chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.47,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:27.89,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it isn't Odokawa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.32,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming to pick you up. Get off work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.64,Italics,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
