Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.73,sign_31113_447_Back,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:44.94,sign_31207_448_Eiji_Kakihana__C,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Eiji Kakihana \N{\fs18}Calling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:47.61,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What is that monkey doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:50.20,sign_31352_450_Kabukicho_Ichiba,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Kabukicho Ichiban-gai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.10,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Odokawa-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:57.46,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to cash \Nyour one billion yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.67,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery Kiss' CD is going \Non sale on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:02.59,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd time it with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:04.99,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pre-order \N300,000 this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:07.86,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,When you think of it that way, \None billion doesn't seem like much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:10.37,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Could you wait a little longer \Nto redeem your ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:13.34,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Some gangsters are after your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:16.39,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! That's super scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.69,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you posted \Nabout it online, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.90,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to change residences \Nand lay low for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:24.55,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Also, is that picture of your \Nwinning lottery ticket still online?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:25.33,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:28.04,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Edit it and re-upload it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:30.31,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Say you actually didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:33.33,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That you wanted to show off. \NPretend you're a pitiful idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:34.74,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Will that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.72,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if this will \Nmake you feel better,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:38.46,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,but you do want to live a long life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:42.37,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can't die until Mystery Kiss \Ntakes over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:44.34,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery Kiss has been \Nthrough a lot of hardship,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.30,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,but their spring's finally on the horizon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:53.68,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Ow. What was that for, Odokawa-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:56.07,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:22:59.85,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Ow. What was that for, Odokawa-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:00.73,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:04.00,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery Kiss' CD is going \Non sale on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:05.93,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd time it with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:08.13,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pre-order \N300,000 this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:10.11,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,When you think of it that way, \None billion doesn't seem like much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:11.49,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's too far back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.87,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't die until Mystery \NKiss takes over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:15.87,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,After that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:18.40,Default,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,Their spring's finally on the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:21.37,Flashback,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,My spring's finally on the horizon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:24.59,sign_28108_321_Kakihana_san____,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,187)}Kakihana-san!! \NGood luck at work
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:24.38,Flashback,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, read it and weep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:30.01,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,How could I forget about that? \NStupid, stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.90,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,She's a calico cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:50.05,Next_Time,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: {\fs22\b1}The Hero's Melancholy{\fs\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:37.96,Italics,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good to see ya, Odokawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:40.34,Italics,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You gettin' enough to drink? \NIs your glass empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:41.36,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:44.64,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Kakihana. What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:47.73,Italics,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All these painful memories \Ncame flooding back...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:49.51,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You sound totally screwed.